You can simply ask Alexa to control your GIA products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our “GIApp” app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “GIApp” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “GIApp” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the air conditioner.
Alexa, turn off the air conditioner.
Alexa, set the air conditioner to 25 degrees.
